cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM 

This paper deals with image-to-illustration translation using generative adversarial networks, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and graphics (cs.GR) sub-categories. The proposed model also involves artificial intelligence techniques (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) to strike a balance between style and content. Additionally, the paper proposes a new evaluation framework for image-to-illustration models, which could fall under multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
